name: Donald Jump - Trump Jumping The Presidential Freedom Border
name_original: Donald Jump - Trump Jumping The Presidential Freedom Border
description:
Donald Jump is here and people are pissed - but who cares, right?!

***** Jump from rooftop to rooftop without falling down!
***** Avoid colliding with the group of people raging in the sky!
***** Collect wigs!
***** Unlock more Donalds! Loads of Donalds for everyone, people!!


So... How far can you get in this crazy satire?!
